proach to the interplay of religious heritage, secularity, economic globalization, militarism, and identity politics in society at large.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 31. Jan 2022) 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Islamic Studies.2bisacsh40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978150362608940uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781503626089423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781503626089/original  aGBV-deGruyter-alles